rComments: She had good lecture slides that really helped explain the material. She seems very helpful in that she sends out emails giving reminders, and hints for hard problems. However she isnt that clear in explaining the material in lecture-you really have to pay attention to understand her. The exams werent too bad either, but the final was challenging.
Good professor. Lecture slides very comprehensive. Always makes sure everyone understands before proceeding.

You won't understand what she is saying for the first 4 weeks after that, not only understand her speaking and her writing gets worse, so you are on your own. Chose the other professor for this class he is so much clear and even fun.
